{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textVariableAnchor"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the renderer chooses the "},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[3, 0]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"code":"text","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"text":" ","type":"text